event CreateGame(address indexed owner, uint256 indexed recordId)
event RoleAdminChanged(bytes32 indexed role, bytes32 indexed previousAdminRole, bytes32 indexed newAdminRole)
event RoleGranted(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
event RoleRevoked(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
event UpdateGame(uint256 indexed recordId, string updatedField)
function create(address owner, tuple(string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website) game, uint8 status)
function getRoleMember(bytes32 role, uint256 index) view returns (address)
function hasRole(bytes32 role, address account) view returns (bool)
function ownerRecordByIndex(address owner, uint256 index) view returns (uint256 recordId)

function recordByIndex(uint256 index) view returns (address owner, tuple(string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website, uint256 createdAt, uint256 updatedAt) game, uint8 status)
